Cards Against Humanity

Packages 
Package Description
ai
The package that contains the classes used in operating the computer players.
ai.data_mining
The package that contains the ai's data mining tools.
ai.nlp
The package that contains the AI's natural language processing tools.
cards
Contains the classes that deal with cards and decks in Cards Against Humanity.
cards.cardpedia
The package that deals with the cardpedia, which will contain information about each card.
game
Contains classes that have to do with the actual game of Cards Against Humanity itself.
graphics
The package that contains all of the graphics and classes that load the graphics for CAH.
import_export
The package that helps import and export files.
netplay  
org.eclipse.wb.swing  
sounds
A package that contains classes that have to do with playing music, which will be made of a playlist, songs agaisnt humanity.
ui
The package that has to do with the user interface for Cards Against Humanity.
users
The package that contains the classes that have to do with users, user information, and keeping records on users so that they can be impersonated by the computer.
